# ChatGPT UI using OpenAI api

## Description
It generates a UI for using chatGPT api. The api key is encoded with a passkey and stored in the repo. So only by knowing the passkey you can decode and use the api.

## Installation
In addition to the available scripts in the [package.json](package.json), you can simply let the workflow defined in [here](.github/workflows/gh-pages.yml) to deploy the production ready of the site to the github pages setup in the settings of your github repo.

## Usage
open the website from your deployed URL and enter the passkey then enjoy the intuitive UI.
